pregunta1.titulo: When and where will Ovum 2022 be held?
pregunta1.texto1: The Ovum 2022 will be held in San Pedro Sula, Honduras from September 6 to 9, 2022

pregunta2.texto1: Registration is open to anyone interested in Ovum 2022. Check registration fees to see this year's registration fees.

pregunta3.titulo: Is simultaneous interpretation service offered during the event?
pregunta3.texto1: Ovum 2022 offers interpretation services in several languages during the opening ceremony, the general sessions and the closing ceremony. Most of the parallel sessions will be held in Spanish, but some of them could also offer this service. Check the event program to check which sessions will have a Spanish interpretation service.

pregunta4.titulo: What is the temperature in Honduras in September?
pregunta4.texto1: In the month of September, temperatures range between 25 and 28 degrees Celsius.
pregunta4.texto2: Since the convention center is air-conditioned, consider bringing a light jacket or sweater.

pregunta5.texto1: Those interested in attending the event can register themselves and their guests online at
pregunta5.texto3: . If you wish, you can also register at the venue of the event

pregunta6.titulo: What is the cost of registration?
pregunta6.texto1: Check the complete box of the registration fees, the types of participants, and what your registration includes.
pregunta6.texto5: How do I register a guest?
pregunta6.texto6: You can add a guest to your registration at

pregunta7.titulo: I canceled my registration, how can I re-register?
pregunta7.texto1: Unfortunately, once the registration is cancelled, it cannot be created again online. If you wish to re-register, you will need to fax or mail the registration and ticket order form.
pregunta7.texto2: The current registration fee will apply.

pregunta8.titulo: What should I do to book a hotel room and what are your rates per night?
pregunta8.texto1: Ovum 2022 offers you different hotels and rates in San Pedro Sula. Click here to see

pregunta9.texto1: Ovum 2022 will provide bus service suitable for people with disabilities, between the official contracted hotels Ovum 2022 and the Convention Center of the Chamber of Commerce and Industries of Cortés.

pregunta10.titulo: Are there other methods of transportation?
pregunta10.texto1: San Pedro Sula has a public transportation system, called the Great Metropolitan Central of San Pedro Sula, the largest and most modern bus terminal in Central America. Taxis and rideshares (including Uber) are also available.

pregunta11.titulo: What should I do to obtain a visa to travel to the event?
pregunta11.texto2: or visit the Department of Honduras website to find out who needs a visa and when to apply, as well as additional information. Visa information varies by country of citizenship. Ovum 2022 provides consulates and embassies with an up-to-date list of registrants for the event and requests that visas be granted to as many registrants as possible, but the granting of such visas is ultimately up to the Honduran government. Ovum 2022 cannot intervene on behalf of individual registrants.

pregunta12.titulo: What immigration requirements are there to enter Honduras?
pregunta12.texto1: -Passengers must carry out an electronic migratory pre-registration, establishing the date of entry and exit to the country.
pregunta12.texto2: -Immunized passengers must carry the original card that was issued to them at the site of application of the vaccine, which must contain the complete dose schedule, with a time later than 14 days from it’s implementation.
pregunta12.texto3: -If you have not been vaccinated, you must upload the result of any test for the detection of COVID-19 accepted in the country: Antigen detection swab and rt-PCR swab. The provision to carry out said test is maintained in a time not greater than seventy-two (72) hours prior to the trip.
pregunta12.texto5: -Passengers of South American origin must carry their yellow fever vaccination card

pregunta13.titulo: What events can I attend during Ovum 2022?
pregunta13.texto1: Convention registration includes the following events:
pregunta13.texto2: Convention Center of the Chamber of Commerce and Industries of Cortés, in the commercial capital of northern Catracho, San Pedro Sula, Honduras from September 6 to 9

Ovum.parrafo1: I am pleased to address you on behalf of the Latin American Poultry Farmers Association and the Honduran National Poultry Farmers Association, as the Organizing Committee of OVUM 2022. We warmly welcome you to San Pedro Sula, thank you for your kind assistance in an unforgettable experience. : The XXVII Latin American Poultry Congress is bringing together scientists, nutritionists, and high-level specialists for the exchange of experiences in matters of health, innovation, animal welfare, safety, and antibiotic-free production for the benefit of the world population.
Ovum.parrafo2: During your stay you will be able to enjoy the Commercial Fair, Scientific Conferences and for the first time in the OVUM a series of very enriching Drills.
Ovum.parrafo3: We are extremely excited to welcome you; Thank you for coming and visiting San Pedro Sula, for being here in Honduras, welcome to the land of the Mayans! A land blessed by its heritage, historical and cultural legacy. A land of inexhaustible tourist attraction, exuberant beaches that conquer the world and, of course, with an extraordinary potential for business. A land of warm, hard-working and enterprising people. A rich and generous land that transcends time and space.
